Single-Click Widget Interactions

You can add single-click interactions to your dashboard widgets to curate data journeys for your users. A single-click in an overview widget takes you directly to a detailed page, opens a lens for cohesive exploration, or starts a flow.

When you click a selection in an overview chart, it opens the details page with your selection applied or opens a lens with filters applied for immediate navigation.

Add interactions to widgets to guide users through multiple levels of data. For example, start at a large scale and navigate a user through more granular areas, such as a business segment or account owner.
